Class CO2FootprintV2

  • java.lang.Object
    • CO2FootprintV2

  • public class CO2FootprintV2
extends java.lang.Object
    This class calculate tons, pounds, and gallons of CO2 based on an initial value in gallons. It contains mutator methods to convert gallons of CO2 to tons, and tons of CO2 to pounds. It contains getter methods to return each private instance variable. Private instance variables include myGallonsUsed, myTonsCO2, myPoundsCO2.
    Version:
    11/18/17
    Author:
    Will English
